[assistant] Fixed the remaining Linux `kernel32` loading issue and amended the commit again.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - Even `Unsafe.allocateInstance(Factory.class)` triggers class initialization.
[assistant] - Initializing `Factory` initializes superclass `ObjectFactory`.
[assistant] - `ObjectFactory` statically calls `Kernel32.INSTANCE.GetUserDefaultLCID()`, which attempts to load Windows `kernel32` and fails on Linux.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Fix:
[assistant] - Added a small in-test JNA `NativeLibrary` cache shim for `kernel32` before `Factory` initialization.
[assistant] - The shim provides only the `GetUserDefaultLCID` / `GetUserDefaultLCIDW` function needed by `ObjectFactory` static initialization.
[assistant] - This keeps the test Linux-compatible while still executing the real `Factory.createProxy(...)` path.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated commit:
[assistant] - `b5a869621d Add JNA Factory proxy coverage test`
[assistant] 
[assistant] Working tree is clean. I did not run tests.
[assistant-event] text_end
[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fixed the remaining Linux `kernel32` loading issue and amended the commit again.\n\nCause:\n- Even `Unsafe.allocateInstance(Factory.class)` triggers class initialization.\n- Initializing `Factory` initializes superclass `ObjectFactory`.\n- `ObjectFactory` statically calls `Kernel32.INSTANCE.GetUserDefaultLCID()`, which attempts to load Windows `kernel32` and fails on Linux.\n\nFix:\n- Added a small in-test JNA `NativeLibrary` cache shim for `kernel32` before `Factory` initialization.\n- The shim provides only the `GetUserDefaultLCID` / `GetUserDefaultLCIDW` function needed by `ObjectFactory` static initialization.\n- This keeps the test Linux-compatible while still executing the real `Factory.createProxy(...)` path.\n\nUpdated commit:\n- `b5a869621d Add JNA Factory proxy coverage test`\n\nWorking tree is clean. I did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03e32479f4cf55c10169f2e013d4c481a28620d8cd44714aa9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 402, "output": 190, "cacheRead": 72192, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 72784, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777524754003, "responseId": "resp_03e32479f4cf55c10169f2e0129f0881a2bdaf77a9fce84900"}}
